comments.body:
Why not this?
```C++
        if (ctx.MsContext() == MiniscriptContext::P2WSH) {
            return GetStackSize() <= MAX_STANDARD_P2WSH_STACK_ITEMS;
        }
```
Otherwise, it seems to add the other condition for the `P2WSH` context as well.

